hopobject.body: I wanted to live abroad buy sinrex canada Of course the long cycle has “ended”, most businesses that are left are already running on skeleton crews and downsized as much as possible without shutting the doors. The layoffs have tapered primarily because there are significantly fewer people working and therefore fewer to layoff, not because business and the economy are getting better. The jobless claims numbers are almost irrelevant as the article eludes to. Lets start reporting the labor force participation number.
